<div class="relative z-10 py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-900 min-h-screen text-gray-200 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div class="max-w-lg w-full">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-5 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 via-red-500 to-pink-500">
                Əlaqə Qurun
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400">
                Suallarınız, təklifləriniz və ya əməkdaşlıq üçün bizimlə əlaqə saxlayın. Sizə kömək etməkdən məmnun olarıq!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-800/60 backdrop-blur-lg border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-2xl">
            <form action="/contact" method="POST"> <!-- Formanın action və method atributlarını backend-ə uyğunlaşdırın -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-6">
                    <div>
                        <label for="full-name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-1">Adınız və Soyadınız</label>
                        <input type="text" name="full-name" id="full-name" autocomplete="name" required
                               class="py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm bg-gray-700/70 border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out"
                               placeholder="Adınız və Soyadınız">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-1">E-poçt Ünvanınız</label>
                        <input id="email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required
                               class="py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm bg-gray-700/70 border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out"
                               placeholder="example@mail.com">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-1">Mesajınız</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required
                                  class="py-3 px-4 block w-full shadow-sm bg-gray-700/70 border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out"
                                  placeholder="Mesajınızı buraya daxil edin..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <button type="submit"
                                class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 border border-transparent rounded-lg shadow-md text-base font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-600 hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-red-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-800 focus:ring-orange-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105">
                            Mesajı Göndər
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
            
            <div class="mt-12 text-center border-t border-gray-700 pt-8">
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">Alternativ olaraq, bizə Discord üzərindən də qoşula bilərsiniz:</p>
                <a href="#" target="_blank" 
                   class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-800 focus:ring-indigo-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.297 4.469c-.188-.562-.656-1.031-1.125-1.219-.562-.281-1.219-.281-1.781 0L12 5.688l-5.391-2.438c-.562-.281-1.219-.281-1.781 0-.469.188-.938.656-1.125 1.219-.188.562-.094 1.219.188 1.688L8.281 12l-4.375 5.844c-.281.469-.375 1.125-.188 1.688.188.562.656 1.031 1.125 1.219.281.094.562.188.844.188.375 0 .656-.094.938-.188L12 18.313l5.391 2.438c.281.094.562.188.938.188.281 0 .562-.094.844-.188.469-.188.938-.656 1.125-1.219.188-.562.094-1.219-.188-1.688L15.719 12l4.375-5.844c.281-.469.375-1.125.188-1.688zM10.125 13.5H7.5V10.5h2.625v3zm6.375 0h-2.625V10.5h2.625v3z"/></svg>
                    Discord Serverimizə Qoşulun
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>